These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, tomato
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, tennis
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person eating tomato##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | tomato   | blueberry  |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, avocado
2 different pets are kept: rat, turtle
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the rat is not the person eating avocado##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | peach | avocado      |
| Pet    | rat  | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
